data.description: Welcome Home!  This 2-story home has everything you need!  Including a 16x32 ft in-ground heated pool.  The pool features a new liner, new furnace, chlorinator, new pump, new winter cover, and solar cover with a spindle.  Enjoy your spring/summer and fall in a brand-new pool!  Fresh paint and new trim throughout for your fresh move-in ready home!  Home has many upgrades to offer.   All new Anderson Energy Star windows.  The basement has been waterproofed and the sump pump was installed in 2023 through Mid-Michigan Basements.  Basement work has a lifetime warranty that is transferrable to the new owners.  The yard has been fully landscaped in the front and back.  Both full bathrooms have been updated in 2023.  The roof is about 8 years old on the home.  All new custom doors in the den, downstairs entry, upstairs hallway, and in all 3 bedrooms.  Come enjoy everything Midland has to offer!  This one won't last long!
